{"tid":1744139,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本兔子天堂: 大久野島","createTime":"2019-11-21T14:24:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T14:41:50.000Z","uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5df5a9a270fec8e034ca7609fba01f625b65697a","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T14:24:51.000Z","msg":"大家有沒有去過<span style=\"color: gold;\">日本「兔仔島」</span>大久野島？這裡有幾千隻自由自在的兔子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjLnNOtD_sOk&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=924c8e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyAoXHKDcW8I&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=946ca63c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I</a><br />\n<br />\n但其實島內, 不是每隻兔子都活得開心和長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predator)威脅，但很多有病, 沒有足夠糧食和營養, 所以兔迷下次去最好帶乾草(Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等)和蔬菜🥬。給牠們最基本的高纖維糧食。不要給高糖份和零食, 例如：蘿蔔、水果。<br />\n<br />\n當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=fc23a565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a><br />\n<br />\n憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=c0ff2b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a><br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。<br />\n<br />\n兔子因生病(痙攣)而憂愁:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=7a957335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊來源:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=d374ef76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me</a>"},{"pid":"83e1b039fb9c3f57aa1cd59c187c9ee8879c6526","tid":1744139,"uid":315545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e724891c7f0501edef3cbbb3dabc816f755f6dc8","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:38:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720fab83807e604a027f0c018179f5a886553bee","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子的食物和份量</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡😊<br />\n- 2湯匙兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙或以下)水果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老兔(6歲以上)：</span><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</span><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養，(而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更多資訊：<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=fdcf370f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"a9229185a820e544d3ed63e4ceb2fef5749b2167","tid":1744139,"uid":13349,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"煮晒黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ab947d3c44cd795c40be7aa878d109311ff30f","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人! ☺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是一種好心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是牠的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=02f5af31\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"094a9f8a32ce23f662352e88ddafd4e947714eab","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子開心到極!&nbsp;🌟🐰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=596c139f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=a4e23d1f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a>"},{"pid":"844d45eca307fa5b56433fdd6d6c4c25bfa0de7d","tid":1744139,"uid":28353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去廣島順便去"},{"pid":"1ba1688a1da23d6db593bf42ced32b004ada43ff","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"844d45eca307fa5b56433fdd6d6c4c25bfa0de7d","tid":1744139,"uid":28353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T12:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去廣島順便去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T13:21:59.000Z","msg":"好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e374ac1e959254328999221a6d60c39ac7a5a4","tid":1744139,"uid":197098,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢同主人玩：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=t5TWSf1rAjisfLcmnBMt89TdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=359552de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"}]}